      "text": "get http https://httpbin.org/json\nwrite to %response%",
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "indent": 0,
      "comment": "Smoke test of Cut 4 at the goal layer. The hard probe (body\u0027s _value\nstays null after the property read) lives in C# HttpChannelTests; this\ngoal test pins the surface: %response!status% reads metadata, the\nsubsequent %response.field% reads the body. Result of the body read\ndepends on the live endpoint; the smoke is that both calls succeed and\nhttp.response no longer exists as a parallel type.",
